title: Chris Wood: South Jersey Trash
description:
The boys a back with a fun one! Comedian Chris Woods sits down Kippy and Foley to talk growing up in New Jersey, Trashy Food, and Living with his parents during the Pandemic. 


Bonus Episodes: www.Patreon.com/AreYouGarbage
